WEBVTT

01:26.300 --> 01:34.970
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.440 --> 01:37.850
[Episode 26]

01:49.479 --> 01:51.009
Mom, you're awake.

01:53.650 --> 01:54.430
Your IV drip is almost done.

01:54.430 --> 01:55.630
I'll go get the nurse.

01:56.060 --> 01:56.870
No need.

01:57.950 --> 01:58.870
The nurse will come on rounds

01:58.870 --> 02:00.370
in a while.

02:01.810 --> 02:03.570
Don't run around, rest a bit.

02:12.060 --> 02:12.800
How have you been feeling

02:12.800 --> 02:14.090
mentally lately?

02:14.680 --> 02:16.400
Your wound keeps getting infected,

02:16.400 --> 02:19.020
and the side effects
of chemotherapy are severe.

02:19.020 --> 02:20.240
I want to consult an expert

02:20.240 --> 02:22.100
to see if there are other options.

02:24.150 --> 02:26.079
I know my body.

02:27.150 --> 02:29.550
I'll be healed and
discharged in a few days.

02:30.900 --> 02:31.829
Be a good girl.

02:33.370 --> 02:34.430
Don't fuss over it.

02:35.370 --> 02:36.840
Don't make me worry.

02:50.900 --> 02:51.760
Zhuang Zhuang,

02:51.960 --> 02:53.840
you must have skipped your meal again.

02:53.840 --> 02:55.240
Come, eat while it's hot.

02:57.180 --> 02:58.180
Thank you, Mr. Ye.

03:00.630 --> 03:01.830
Don't worry too much.

03:04.520 --> 03:05.240
I still have

03:05.620 --> 03:07.500
friends who can lend us some money.

03:07.500 --> 03:08.780
If all else fails...

03:09.630 --> 03:10.930
Our shop

03:11.030 --> 03:12.490
can be sold for some money.

03:19.340 --> 03:19.800
Over the years,

03:19.800 --> 03:21.079
most of your savings

03:22.530 --> 03:24.079
have been spent on my singing.

03:24.079 --> 03:25.410
That's how it should be.

03:26.410 --> 03:27.140
Your mom just

03:27.530 --> 03:28.960
wants to be by your side.

03:29.360 --> 03:30.740
It's no use persuading her.

03:30.740 --> 03:32.270
You need to understand her.

03:33.960 --> 03:34.820
How about this?

03:35.190 --> 03:37.310
I'll go see what the expert says tomorrow.

03:37.310 --> 03:37.870
Okay.

03:39.850 --> 03:41.850
If we really have to sell the shop...

03:44.690 --> 03:46.810
Once our family gets through
this difficult time,

03:46.810 --> 03:48.470
I will definitely buy it back.

03:49.930 --> 03:50.360
Okay.

03:52.720 --> 03:53.310
Eat up.

04:07.890 --> 04:09.910
The surgery went reasonably well.

04:10.750 --> 04:12.430
But for your mother,

04:12.520 --> 04:13.920
at her age,

04:14.460 --> 04:16.519
postoperative recovery is crucial.

04:17.120 --> 04:18.740
If she doesn't recover well,

04:19.540 --> 04:21.000
it's very easy to relapse.

04:21.540 --> 04:22.540
Given this situation,

04:22.540 --> 04:24.270
will she need another surgery?

04:25.070 --> 04:27.180
Another open-chest surgery is too risky.

04:27.180 --> 04:29.640
We can only treat it
conservatively for now.

04:30.680 --> 04:31.540
How about this?

04:31.570 --> 04:32.720
I'll prescribe a medication

04:32.720 --> 04:33.850
called interferon.

04:34.310 --> 04:36.290
It is one of the classic drugs

04:36.330 --> 04:37.930
for adjuvant therapy
after tumor chemotherapy

04:37.930 --> 04:39.390
and surgery.

04:39.830 --> 04:40.860
It can effectively

04:40.860 --> 04:42.659
inhibit the spread of the tumor.

04:43.000 --> 04:44.460
It's just a bit expensive.

04:45.010 --> 04:46.870
Currently, our hospital's supply

04:46.870 --> 04:47.830
is all imported.

04:48.570 --> 04:49.970
One course of treatment

04:50.060 --> 04:51.060
costs over 4,000.

04:51.870 --> 04:52.700
You should

04:52.860 --> 04:53.420
decide based on

04:53.420 --> 04:54.890
your family's

04:54.930 --> 04:55.920
specific circumstances.

04:55.920 --> 04:56.310
Okay?

04:59.920 --> 05:00.720
I understand.

05:01.370 --> 05:03.370
Please prescribe it for me, doctor.

05:39.560 --> 05:41.180
Domestically processed goods.

05:41.180 --> 05:43.770
Russian cowhide is of
particularly high quality.

05:43.770 --> 05:45.130
We can ship the raw materials from Russia

05:45.130 --> 05:47.680
to China for processing before
selling them back to them.

05:47.680 --> 05:49.409
The profit margin is very high.

05:49.680 --> 05:51.500
I'm telling you, it's promising.

05:51.500 --> 05:52.280
Take a look.

06:01.330 --> 06:02.240
Welcome, listeners,

06:02.240 --> 06:03.370
to our station

06:03.370 --> 06:04.330
at the 14th

06:04.330 --> 06:05.500
Youth Singing Competition

06:05.500 --> 06:06.510
finals.

06:06.930 --> 06:07.890
This final

06:08.010 --> 06:09.430
will be broadcast live,

06:09.570 --> 06:10.560
sharing this auditory feast

06:10.560 --> 06:11.880
with the audience.

06:12.540 --> 06:14.380
Alright, the host is now

06:14.450 --> 06:15.500
backstage.

06:15.570 --> 06:16.770
The contestants are making

06:16.770 --> 06:18.300
their final preparations.

06:41.830 --> 06:42.180
Uncle.

06:42.180 --> 06:42.750
Why is your cough

06:42.750 --> 06:43.690
getting worse?

06:46.620 --> 06:47.370
Blood.

06:47.850 --> 06:48.950
You coughed up blood, Uncle.

06:48.950 --> 06:51.280
Let me take you
to the hospital right away.

06:55.100 --> 06:56.360
I have weathered

06:56.390 --> 06:57.270
many storms.

06:58.010 --> 06:59.040
This is just a minor issue.

06:59.040 --> 07:00.170
Why go to a hospital?

07:00.270 --> 07:01.330
Tell me, what is it?

07:04.890 --> 07:07.530
There is a very capable person

07:07.950 --> 07:10.060
who wants to arrange a meeting with you.

07:10.060 --> 07:11.360
Do I need to worry

07:12.160 --> 07:13.760
about such a trivial matter?

07:14.430 --> 07:16.800
You have already
learned everything from me.

07:16.800 --> 07:19.430
Just unleash your imagination,

07:19.690 --> 07:21.220
let go of your constraints,

07:21.540 --> 07:22.950
and go do it boldly.

07:25.540 --> 07:25.920
Go.

07:28.750 --> 07:29.100
Go.

07:40.040 --> 07:41.620
Chu Caiyuan, I have made it

07:41.620 --> 07:42.500
very clear to you.

07:42.500 --> 07:44.170
Please do not call me again,

07:44.680 --> 07:46.680
and don't send anyone to look for me.

07:47.659 --> 07:48.390
Even if you come,

07:48.390 --> 07:49.420
I will not see you.

08:21.570 --> 08:22.370
Ranran.

08:30.750 --> 08:31.270
Mr. Guo,

08:32.110 --> 08:33.860
you're here to bring me things again?

08:33.860 --> 08:35.549
Well, your aunt said

08:35.549 --> 08:38.130
you didn't eat much tonight,

08:38.250 --> 08:39.650
so she made you some soup.

08:40.789 --> 08:41.909
See if you like it.

08:42.890 --> 08:44.120
Come, try it.

08:44.530 --> 08:45.540
Mr. Guo,

08:45.670 --> 08:46.740
tell Auntie

08:46.770 --> 08:47.940
not to trouble herself anymore.

08:47.940 --> 08:49.720
Don't be polite with us.

08:50.630 --> 08:52.700
Your aunt cares about you.

08:56.080 --> 08:57.340
Have a seat, Mr. Guo.

09:03.460 --> 09:04.260
What's wrong?

09:05.390 --> 09:06.620
Your aunt told me

09:07.240 --> 09:08.320
that lately,

09:08.840 --> 09:09.620
you've been

09:10.100 --> 09:11.320
avoiding everyone

09:11.320 --> 09:12.370
and feeling down.

09:13.270 --> 09:15.290
Are you just in a bad mood,

09:15.290 --> 09:16.690
or did something happen?

09:16.820 --> 09:19.100
If something's wrong, tell us.

09:19.440 --> 09:21.100
We'll figure it out together.

09:22.030 --> 09:23.150
I'm fine.

09:24.200 --> 09:25.320
Don't worry.

09:30.370 --> 09:31.410
Are you not

09:31.410 --> 09:32.940
filming your show anymore?

09:33.100 --> 09:34.160
I'm done with that.

09:34.440 --> 09:35.570
It's all wrapped up?

09:35.670 --> 09:36.750
That's a good thing.

09:36.750 --> 09:38.010
You should be happy.

09:41.460 --> 09:42.100
Mr. Guo,

09:43.960 --> 09:45.050
I probably

09:46.500 --> 09:48.580
won't act anymore in the future.

09:49.700 --> 09:51.770
Is it because of that boss?

09:59.050 --> 10:00.150
Have the invitations been sent out?

10:00.150 --> 10:01.390
They've all been sent.

10:01.390 --> 10:02.460
How are the preparations for the banquet?

10:02.460 --> 10:04.790
Everything is arranged as you requested.

10:05.130 --> 10:06.320
Pay attention to the details.

10:06.320 --> 10:08.290
Details often determine everything.

10:08.290 --> 10:10.420
The key to success lies in the details.

10:10.460 --> 10:11.930
Don't, don't pull me.

10:12.080 --> 10:12.810
Chu Caiyuan!

10:13.200 --> 10:13.860
You go first.

10:13.860 --> 10:14.320
Get out.

10:14.440 --> 10:15.500
What are you doing?

10:16.790 --> 10:17.720
I'm sorry, Boss.

10:17.980 --> 10:19.110
I couldn't stop him.

10:19.390 --> 10:19.920
Go first.

10:21.750 --> 10:22.410
Who are you?

10:23.150 --> 10:24.550
I'm Shen Ranran's uncle.

10:26.670 --> 10:27.600
What do you want?

10:27.670 --> 10:29.670
She doesn't want to see you anymore.

10:30.410 --> 10:32.340
Stop pestering her.

10:35.290 --> 10:37.150
If you really are Ranran's uncle,

10:37.320 --> 10:38.250
you should know

10:39.050 --> 10:40.780
that this is between the 2 of us,

10:41.030 --> 10:41.550
right?

10:42.270 --> 10:43.930
Then you should also know that

10:43.940 --> 10:45.170
in a matter between 2 people,

10:45.170 --> 10:46.410
when 1 person decides,

10:46.410 --> 10:47.720
it's decided.

10:51.270 --> 10:51.900
Fine.

10:52.550 --> 10:54.030
If this is Ranran's wish,

10:54.670 --> 10:55.360
I agree.

10:56.480 --> 10:57.050
But I must

10:57.050 --> 10:58.510
hear it from her in person.

10:59.170 --> 11:00.300
That's impossible.

11:01.910 --> 11:02.970
If I want to see her,

11:03.860 --> 11:05.060
I have plenty of ways.

11:08.910 --> 11:09.340
Here.

11:09.960 --> 11:12.560
Remember to keep
this medicine refrigerated.

11:14.460 --> 11:15.260
Actually,

11:15.480 --> 11:16.530
our hospital got a batch

11:16.530 --> 11:17.590
of new interferon.

11:17.600 --> 11:19.260
It's domestically produced.

11:20.620 --> 11:21.270
If you're seeing

11:21.270 --> 11:22.550
the specialist for a follow-up later,

11:22.550 --> 11:23.360
ask him

11:23.510 --> 11:25.110
if you can use this medicine.

11:27.580 --> 11:28.290
I see you come to buy medicine

11:28.290 --> 11:29.070
every week,

11:29.100 --> 11:30.220
and it's quite expensive.

11:30.220 --> 11:31.620
This medicine is domestically produced.

11:31.620 --> 11:32.960
If you can use it,

11:33.000 --> 11:34.260
it'll be much cheaper.

11:34.890 --> 11:35.620
However,

11:35.890 --> 11:37.500
our hospital doesn't have much of it,

11:37.500 --> 11:39.290
so you have to find a way
to get it prescribed.

11:39.290 --> 11:40.460
Go ask the specialist

11:40.460 --> 11:42.120
if he can prescribe it for you.

11:42.740 --> 11:43.740
Can I borrow a pen?

11:43.740 --> 11:45.270
I want to write down
the manufacturer's name.

11:45.270 --> 11:46.460
Just take the medicine box.

11:46.460 --> 11:47.410
The box is empty.

11:49.080 --> 11:49.870
Thank you.

11:53.940 --> 11:54.700
Zouwen.

11:54.820 --> 11:55.720
Here's the thing.

11:55.720 --> 11:56.960
My friend is in a lot of debt

11:56.960 --> 11:59.090
and wants to borrow some money from you.

11:59.090 --> 12:00.530
It's a lot, yes.

12:00.980 --> 12:01.840
Well, how much?

12:02.170 --> 12:02.770
300,000.

12:05.580 --> 12:06.200
Wen.

12:06.200 --> 12:07.460
Well, my friend was kidding.

12:07.460 --> 12:08.050
It's a joke.

12:08.050 --> 12:08.550
Sorry.

12:08.550 --> 12:09.340
Sorry to bother you.

12:09.340 --> 12:10.390
I'll treat you to a meal later.

12:10.390 --> 12:11.920
Wish you good fortune. Bye.

12:12.220 --> 12:13.080
300,000?

12:13.320 --> 12:14.910
You asked me to get 300,000 for you?

12:14.910 --> 12:16.510
Do I look like 300,000 to you?

12:16.870 --> 12:17.840
What did you do?

12:17.870 --> 12:19.130
How could you owe 300,000?

12:19.130 --> 12:21.470
I'm not asking to borrow 300,000 from you.

12:21.940 --> 12:23.600
I want to do business with you

12:23.670 --> 12:24.800
to earn 300,000.

12:24.840 --> 12:26.310
I'm in so much debt now.

12:26.370 --> 12:27.150
If I borrow from friends again,

12:27.150 --> 12:27.670
wouldn't that just be

12:27.670 --> 12:29.130
robbing Peter to pay Paul?

12:30.360 --> 12:31.150
Here's the thing.

12:31.150 --> 12:32.360
The business we can do

12:32.360 --> 12:33.500
is nothing more than buying and selling.

12:33.500 --> 12:33.980
Buying and selling can only

12:33.980 --> 12:35.170
make tens of thousands a year.

12:35.170 --> 12:36.770
How many years would it take?

12:39.860 --> 12:40.920
Have you seen this?

12:45.960 --> 12:46.690
Raw cowhide.

12:49.050 --> 12:50.200
Smells like mutton. From Russia?

12:50.200 --> 12:50.580
Yes.

12:51.000 --> 12:51.340
This stuff

12:51.340 --> 12:52.460
is everywhere in Russia.

12:52.460 --> 12:53.000
Yeah.

12:53.630 --> 12:54.130
Because

12:54.150 --> 12:55.810
it's everywhere in Russia,

12:56.030 --> 12:56.840
its price

12:56.840 --> 12:58.520
is a third of that in China.

12:58.650 --> 13:00.310
Two dollars a kilo.

13:00.630 --> 13:01.820
We buy the hide back,

13:01.820 --> 13:03.030
make it into leather shoes and clothes,

13:03.030 --> 13:04.090
and resell it.

13:04.120 --> 13:05.050
I calculated it.

13:06.000 --> 13:08.080
The profit is over 300%.

13:09.030 --> 13:10.530
Your calculation is wrong.

13:10.530 --> 13:12.200
You still need to find a factory

13:12.200 --> 13:13.550
to process and make it.

13:13.600 --> 13:14.790
The factories are all booked now.

13:14.790 --> 13:15.790
We can't get a slot at all.

13:15.790 --> 13:16.990
I've found a factory.

13:17.270 --> 13:19.500
But they are in a similar situation to us.

13:19.500 --> 13:20.320
And what's our situation?

13:20.320 --> 13:21.580
We're short on money.

13:23.820 --> 13:24.650
You've found the factory

13:24.650 --> 13:25.910
and the raw materials.

13:26.460 --> 13:27.480
Then you can do this alone.

13:27.480 --> 13:28.880
You don't need to find me.

13:28.960 --> 13:29.690
That's true.

13:30.150 --> 13:31.950
You've come to the right person.

13:32.370 --> 13:33.780
Find Lucky, get lucky.

13:34.320 --> 13:36.650
We are really suited
for doing business together,

13:36.650 --> 13:36.940
aren't we?

13:36.940 --> 13:38.270
Look at your strong body

13:38.290 --> 13:39.250
and my smart brain.

13:39.250 --> 13:39.820
Right?

13:39.820 --> 13:40.340
No, what do you mean?

13:40.340 --> 13:42.270
My brain isn't smart enough?

13:42.290 --> 13:43.950
It's smart enough. Very good.

13:44.130 --> 13:45.130
Well...

13:45.320 --> 13:46.250
Let's do it.

13:46.320 --> 13:46.920
Yes, deal.

13:47.740 --> 13:49.600
Where are the factory employees?

13:50.130 --> 13:50.700
Wenzhou.

13:52.390 --> 13:53.320
That's a bit far.

13:54.500 --> 13:55.150
Do we have to

13:55.150 --> 13:56.270
go to the factory to have a look?

13:56.270 --> 13:56.870
We have to.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.210
When are we leaving?

13:58.670 --> 13:59.250
The 8th.

14:02.150 --> 14:02.790
Since you're here today,

14:02.790 --> 14:03.940
I must treat you to something.

14:03.940 --> 14:05.010
We have to celebrate.

14:05.010 --> 14:06.470
Let's go. Don't just talk.

14:06.580 --> 14:07.530
Let's go.

14:07.750 --> 14:09.150
What should we eat?

14:09.790 --> 14:10.960
Have you tried the

14:10.960 --> 14:12.000
douzhi downstairs?

14:12.000 --> 14:12.460
Douzhi?

14:12.510 --> 14:13.620
The taste is very authentic.

14:13.620 --> 14:14.240
Forget about the douzhi.

14:14.240 --> 14:15.440
Think it's too cheap?

14:16.270 --> 14:16.930
Wait for me.

14:17.760 --> 14:18.660
[Office Building]

14:19.750 --> 14:22.110
[Office building]

14:24.720 --> 14:28.080
[Oujiang Leather Processing Factory]

14:33.050 --> 14:34.380
Everyone, listen to me.

14:34.410 --> 14:35.840
I didn't run away.

14:36.670 --> 14:38.080
I'm right here.

14:38.620 --> 14:39.740
It's not that I don't want

14:39.740 --> 14:41.050
to pay you.

14:41.200 --> 14:42.010
You all know how little profit

14:42.010 --> 14:43.050
the factory is making.

14:43.050 --> 14:44.580
The machine is also broken.

14:44.740 --> 14:46.670
It costs money to hire someone to fix it.

14:46.670 --> 14:47.550
Just wait until I hire a worker

14:47.550 --> 14:48.610
to fix the machine.

14:48.650 --> 14:50.250
As long as we take the first order

14:50.250 --> 14:50.980
and make some money,

14:50.980 --> 14:52.340
I will deliver the money

14:52.360 --> 14:53.960
door to door in person, okay?

14:54.000 --> 14:55.060
I bow to you all.

14:55.150 --> 14:55.960
Go on back.

14:56.960 --> 14:58.070
One last week.

14:58.240 --> 14:59.220
One last week.

15:00.340 --> 15:01.260
One last week.

15:01.440 --> 15:04.470
[Oujiang Leather Processing Factory]

15:01.500 --> 15:03.440
Everyone, please wait at home for now.

15:03.440 --> 15:04.250
Please head back.

15:04.250 --> 15:04.840
Thank you.

15:04.840 --> 15:05.570
Wait at home.

15:05.770 --> 15:07.100
You will get your money.

15:11.000 --> 15:11.580
Well...

15:12.180 --> 15:14.360
[Oujiang Leather Processing Factory]

15:16.250 --> 15:18.270
That's my bag. There's no money inside.

15:18.270 --> 15:19.200
What's going on?

15:19.550 --> 15:21.320
Are you collecting debts
or taking my life?

15:21.320 --> 15:22.530
Neither.

15:22.750 --> 15:24.290
We are from Beijing.

15:24.480 --> 15:25.410
Here to save you.

15:26.320 --> 15:27.120
Save me?

15:27.790 --> 15:28.200
Yes.

15:28.740 --> 15:30.540
We have an order for you.

15:30.630 --> 15:31.160
An order?

15:34.550 --> 15:36.010
Did you bring the deposit?

15:37.220 --> 15:38.700
We have no cash, but...

15:40.320 --> 15:41.850
We have a way to make it work.

15:45.700 --> 15:46.560
Take a look.

15:46.790 --> 15:48.130
This is Vladivostok cowhide,

15:48.130 --> 15:50.670
quick-frozen at minus 40 degrees.

15:51.550 --> 15:53.200
Look at the pores inside.

15:53.200 --> 15:55.130
They are finer than a needle's eye.

15:55.960 --> 15:56.890
It's good stuff.

16:00.080 --> 16:01.030
Imported material?

16:01.030 --> 16:01.440
Right.

16:02.390 --> 16:03.250
Export orders?

16:03.250 --> 16:03.780
Exactly.

16:04.980 --> 16:06.910
I've seen too much of this. Go back.

16:07.350 --> 16:08.560
Wait a minute.

16:09.000 --> 16:10.890
Don't just run away. Seriously.

16:11.270 --> 16:12.940
What's up with you guys?

16:13.740 --> 16:15.700
Factory 2 ordered
Russian material last year.

16:15.700 --> 16:17.500
When the truck came back
and they uncovered it,

16:17.500 --> 16:19.360
it was all rotten like moldy tofu.

16:19.840 --> 16:20.890
The middleman dealers must have

16:20.890 --> 16:22.600
splashed salt water to add weight.

16:22.600 --> 16:24.130
But you've seen our leather.

16:24.130 --> 16:25.390
This is just the cowhide.

16:25.390 --> 16:26.850
We also have buffalo hide.

16:27.080 --> 16:27.750
How about this?

16:27.750 --> 16:29.330
When you inspect the goods,

16:29.750 --> 16:31.130
if there is even 1 bad piece of leather,

16:31.130 --> 16:32.750
we'll call it quits, okay?

16:34.980 --> 16:36.510
How should I put this to you?

16:38.440 --> 16:39.200
Young man.

16:39.960 --> 16:41.250
From your posture,

16:41.620 --> 16:43.950
this is your first time doing this, right?

16:44.250 --> 16:44.750
Yes.

16:45.220 --> 16:46.350
Let me tell you this.

16:46.840 --> 16:49.100
These export orders are not that simple.

16:49.170 --> 16:50.930
When your goods arrive there,

16:51.170 --> 16:52.740
you are no longer in control.

16:52.740 --> 16:54.130
Let's not even talk about the payment.

16:54.130 --> 16:56.320
It'd be good enough if you could come back

16:56.320 --> 16:57.050
in one piece.

16:57.650 --> 16:59.170
So many people have failed there.

16:59.170 --> 16:59.770
What?

17:00.370 --> 17:02.830
You 2 still want to
throw yourselves into it?

17:04.000 --> 17:05.270
Well, my old friend.

17:05.270 --> 17:06.829
You don't know who I am.

17:07.069 --> 17:07.880
My name is Lucky Ma.

17:07.880 --> 17:08.940
I do trade in Russia

17:08.940 --> 17:09.680
all year round.

17:09.680 --> 17:11.329
Look at me, I'm perfectly fine, aren't I?

17:11.329 --> 17:12.869
And let me tell you,

17:12.920 --> 17:13.910
I keep my word.

17:13.930 --> 17:15.200
If I say I'll pay you,
I will definitely pay you.

17:15.200 --> 17:16.230
My words are solid like nails.

17:16.230 --> 17:17.589
Like the date pits Qiu Qianchi

17:17.589 --> 17:18.790
spat out in the story.

17:18.980 --> 17:19.380
Right?

17:19.609 --> 17:20.510
Just trust me.

17:20.530 --> 17:22.190
If not, we can sign a contract.

17:22.420 --> 17:22.810
I thought

17:22.810 --> 17:24.720
you were going to spit date pits at me.

17:24.720 --> 17:26.030
We heard that in 1983,

17:26.380 --> 17:27.790
this factory was not doing well.

17:27.790 --> 17:29.050
You were the youngest factory director

17:29.050 --> 17:30.110
at the time,

17:30.330 --> 17:31.730
and you were an outsider.

17:31.830 --> 17:33.420
You led everyone together,

17:33.530 --> 17:34.420
worked 3 shifts a day,

17:34.420 --> 17:36.180
and relied on those old machines.

17:36.180 --> 17:36.940
Despite that, you completed

17:36.940 --> 17:38.750
your first
foreign trade order, didn't you?

17:38.750 --> 17:39.810
Back then, everyone

17:39.810 --> 17:40.810
got a dividend.

17:41.440 --> 17:43.330
Don't you want to rely on
foreign trade orders

17:43.330 --> 17:44.790
to save the factory again?

17:45.830 --> 17:46.720
When you get to a place,

17:45.990 --> 17:49.340
[Old Wenzhou Specialty Snack Shop]

17:46.750 --> 17:47.330
you have to eat

17:47.330 --> 17:48.550
their local food.

17:48.880 --> 17:50.300
This is called "When in Rome,
do as the Romans do,"

17:50.300 --> 17:51.060
you know?

17:51.140 --> 17:52.610
Like these Wenzhou fish balls

17:52.610 --> 17:53.330
and this dried rice noodle,

17:53.330 --> 17:54.400
they are all very famous.

17:54.400 --> 17:55.290
What we're eating now

17:55.290 --> 17:56.590
is called pork offal noodles.

17:56.590 --> 17:57.830
Here are your pork offal noodles.

17:57.830 --> 17:58.960
-Thank you.
-Enjoy.

17:59.290 --> 18:00.510
Thank you.

18:01.290 --> 18:02.030
Pork offal noodles.

18:02.030 --> 18:02.480
Right.

18:03.110 --> 18:04.110
It's not dirty at all.

18:04.110 --> 18:05.240
It's as clean as I am.

18:07.010 --> 18:07.820
Oh, right.

18:07.960 --> 18:09.120
About the factory equipment,

18:09.120 --> 18:10.180
we both took a look.

18:13.620 --> 18:14.350
It's not bad.

18:15.240 --> 18:16.270
Their factory equipment

18:16.270 --> 18:17.870
is really good.

18:19.590 --> 18:20.220
You can tell that

18:20.220 --> 18:21.780
they spent a lot of money
on it in the early years.

18:21.780 --> 18:23.110
But the problem is that
the machines are abandoned,

18:23.110 --> 18:23.850
and there are no workers.

18:23.850 --> 18:24.290
So we need

18:24.290 --> 18:26.020
a solution for those problems.

18:26.180 --> 18:26.940
I heard from Liangliang that

18:26.940 --> 18:28.880
when you were acting
as a middleman before,

18:28.880 --> 18:29.900
you knew a key technical staff member

18:29.900 --> 18:30.960
from some factory.

18:31.010 --> 18:31.790
What was the name of that factory again?

18:31.790 --> 18:33.310
The factory was called...

18:33.660 --> 18:34.750
Yes. That person's surname is Pan.

18:34.750 --> 18:37.290
His name is Pan... Pan...

18:37.980 --> 18:39.300
Pan Shi or something.

18:39.400 --> 18:41.460
-Mr. Pan. The chief.
-Yes, the chief.

18:42.010 --> 18:43.220
Can you invite him over?

18:43.220 --> 18:44.080
I probably can.

18:44.200 --> 18:45.200
I'll give it a try.

18:45.240 --> 18:46.900
Actually, he really hates businessmen.

18:46.900 --> 18:47.640
After the businessmen

18:47.640 --> 18:48.570
went to his place,

18:48.570 --> 18:49.960
they fired all his colleagues

18:49.960 --> 18:51.270
and only kept the technical team,

18:51.270 --> 18:51.880
making it seem like

18:51.880 --> 18:53.240
the team had betrayed the masses.

18:53.240 --> 18:54.300
That's great.

18:54.460 --> 18:56.270
Then I'll leave this to you, Jun.

18:56.680 --> 18:58.030
As for the workers,

18:58.420 --> 18:59.620
that will cost money.

18:59.660 --> 19:01.900
I'll go back to Beijing
and figure out a way.

19:01.900 --> 19:03.430
Look at what you're saying.

19:03.570 --> 19:04.940
You're leaving this to me?

19:04.940 --> 19:06.090
You really act like

19:06.090 --> 19:06.890
a big boss now.

19:07.240 --> 19:07.700
I feel like

19:07.700 --> 19:09.440
you're more like a businessman than I am.

19:09.440 --> 19:10.500
No.

19:10.850 --> 19:12.900
Only you can get this done, Jun.

19:13.140 --> 19:15.670
If it were me,
I wouldn't be able to invite him.

19:16.570 --> 19:17.420
To be honest, I really think

19:17.420 --> 19:19.180
you're smarter than Liangliang.

19:19.180 --> 19:19.740
Liangliang and I

19:19.740 --> 19:20.720
are just not compatible
for making money.

19:20.720 --> 19:21.140
Why?

19:21.180 --> 19:21.720
I'm Mr. Lucky,

19:21.720 --> 19:22.480
and he's Liangliang.

19:22.480 --> 19:23.350
Listen to the names.

19:23.350 --> 19:24.440
"Lucky Liang" sounds like

19:24.440 --> 19:25.460
"Luck has gone cold" instead.

19:25.460 --> 19:26.220
We are different.

19:26.220 --> 19:27.140
Your name means victory.

19:27.140 --> 19:28.500
So we're Lucky and Victory, right?

19:28.500 --> 19:29.380
It sounds auspicious.

19:29.380 --> 19:30.240
Lucky Victory.

19:30.680 --> 19:31.780
And I think Wenzhou

19:31.900 --> 19:32.850
is a pretty good place.

19:32.850 --> 19:33.910
It gathers wealth.

19:35.160 --> 19:35.460
Yes.

19:35.460 --> 19:37.000
I think the address is from Huzhou.

19:37.000 --> 19:38.050
Can you ask for me?

19:39.290 --> 19:39.750
Okay.

19:40.400 --> 19:42.660
I'll definitely find a way to ask for you.

19:42.740 --> 19:43.380
Zhuang,

19:44.610 --> 19:45.680
are you alright?

19:45.740 --> 19:46.380
I'm fine.

19:47.330 --> 19:48.390
Are you doing okay?

19:48.570 --> 19:49.500
I'm doing great.

19:50.160 --> 19:51.830
Zhuang, if anything really happens,

19:51.830 --> 19:53.240
you must tell me.

19:53.590 --> 19:54.900
We can figure it out together.

19:54.900 --> 19:56.560
Don't worry, I'm really fine.

19:58.890 --> 20:00.420
About me calling you,

20:00.570 --> 20:01.720
don't tell Xu, okay?

20:02.510 --> 20:04.480
What's wrong? Did you two fight?

20:04.750 --> 20:05.330
No.

20:06.140 --> 20:07.270
Just reminding you.

20:07.570 --> 20:08.500
I'll hang up now.

20:24.650 --> 20:26.340
I hear you, I hear you.

20:26.680 --> 20:27.510
Let me think about

20:27.510 --> 20:28.670
how to tell him.

20:30.980 --> 20:31.880
Two minutes

20:31.880 --> 20:32.610
are almost up.

20:32.610 --> 20:33.970
I'm hanging up.

21:09.250 --> 21:10.780
What's the meaning of this?

21:12.590 --> 21:13.420
I gave it all to you.

21:13.420 --> 21:14.550
Here's another 500.

21:17.000 --> 21:18.160
Don't mind the smell.

21:18.160 --> 21:20.680
Seriously, what's the meaning of this?

21:21.530 --> 21:23.700
Liangliang called me

21:23.700 --> 21:24.530
and said...

21:26.400 --> 21:28.260
Let me think about how to tell you.

21:28.790 --> 21:30.390
Let me organize my thoughts.

21:31.520 --> 21:33.290
Zhuang Zhuang and you...

21:33.940 --> 21:36.070
Zhuang Zhuang is from Wenzhou, right?

21:40.500 --> 21:42.030
Have you contacted her recently?

21:42.030 --> 21:42.590
No.

21:43.980 --> 21:44.820
Why not?

21:45.030 --> 21:46.830
She doesn't want me to.

21:47.950 --> 21:49.460
You sure care a lot about this.

21:49.460 --> 21:50.700
Okay, if that's your attitude,

21:50.700 --> 21:52.850
then I'll just tell you.

21:53.720 --> 21:54.420
Liangliang called.

21:54.420 --> 21:55.530
We were talking about something else,

21:55.530 --> 21:56.290
and he happened to mention

21:56.290 --> 21:58.690
that Zhuang Zhuang was looking for Ranran.

21:59.480 --> 22:01.170
She called Ranran to ask

22:01.310 --> 22:03.170
about a pharmaceutical factory.

22:03.770 --> 22:05.500
What pharmaceutical factory?

22:06.240 --> 22:06.970
Interferon.

22:08.460 --> 22:10.180
What is an interferon?

22:12.400 --> 22:13.380
Well...

22:15.700 --> 22:16.480
If I tell you,

22:16.480 --> 22:17.440
don't get mad.

22:18.330 --> 22:19.380
Then don't tell me.

22:19.380 --> 22:20.050
Don't tell me.

22:20.050 --> 22:20.940
How can I not tell you?

22:20.940 --> 22:21.680
I'm your bro.

22:22.380 --> 22:24.110
Shouldn't I comfort you first?

22:25.550 --> 22:26.660
Interferon is...

22:27.500 --> 22:28.830
You know cancer, right?

22:29.240 --> 22:30.430
Interferon is

22:30.740 --> 22:32.140
an adjuvant therapy drug

22:32.240 --> 22:34.300
for post-surgery cancer treatment.

22:39.180 --> 22:39.640
Money.

22:39.640 --> 22:40.630
Take the money.

22:40.740 --> 22:41.600
Take the money.

22:42.090 --> 22:42.770
Be careful.

22:42.770 --> 22:44.430
Let me know if it's not enough.

23:29.810 --> 23:30.950
Give me a cabbage.

23:31.070 --> 23:31.720
Cabbage.

23:34.730 --> 23:36.050
And a bit of this vegetable too.

23:36.050 --> 23:36.530
Okay.

23:37.050 --> 23:37.910
Help yourself.

23:38.310 --> 23:39.040
Here's a bag.

23:50.610 --> 23:51.370
Eight taels.

24:01.500 --> 24:02.360
Zhuang Zhuang.

24:34.090 --> 24:35.020
Long time no see.

24:40.610 --> 24:41.410
How are you?

24:58.750 --> 25:00.010
Why are you in Wenzhou?

25:01.760 --> 25:02.750
Xiaojun and I came here

25:02.750 --> 25:03.940
to do some business.

25:07.310 --> 25:09.240
Are you not making movies anymore?

25:10.500 --> 25:11.720
Movie production cycles are long,

25:11.720 --> 25:13.110
and there's post-production to wait for.

25:13.110 --> 25:14.180
I was just thinking

25:14.660 --> 25:16.460
of making some money in between.

25:18.460 --> 25:19.190
That's good.

25:19.290 --> 25:20.020
That's good.

25:21.240 --> 25:22.170
Is it going well?

25:22.780 --> 25:24.580
Very well.

25:25.400 --> 25:26.740
It's just that the factory I found

25:26.740 --> 25:28.670
doesn't have the best conditions.

25:29.290 --> 25:30.550
We can't get enough workers.

25:30.550 --> 25:31.240
So I thought

25:31.250 --> 25:33.010
I'd go back to Beijing
to figure something out.

25:33.010 --> 25:34.140
Do you need any help?

25:40.960 --> 25:41.940
I mean,

25:42.440 --> 25:43.210
my uncle

25:43.570 --> 25:44.220
is a veteran worker

25:44.220 --> 25:45.820
at the textile factory here.

25:47.090 --> 25:48.960
He knows some people

25:48.960 --> 25:50.760
at the leather and cotton mills.

25:59.490 --> 26:00.930
If you need any help,

26:01.110 --> 26:02.040
just let me know.

26:04.940 --> 26:05.820
Can I

26:06.200 --> 26:07.200
go with you later?

26:14.810 --> 26:16.470
Your mother helped me before.

26:16.840 --> 26:18.030
I want to go see her.

26:24.420 --> 26:25.090
Okay.

26:39.750 --> 26:41.790
From your voice on the phone,

26:42.200 --> 26:43.110
I thought

26:43.380 --> 26:44.910
you must be very energetic.

26:46.290 --> 26:47.150
I didn't expect

26:47.570 --> 26:49.210
you'd be even more handsome

26:49.770 --> 26:50.790
than I imagined.

26:53.140 --> 26:53.680
Auntie,

26:54.420 --> 26:56.420
I should have come to see you sooner.

26:56.940 --> 26:59.070
But I've been running around for work,

26:59.070 --> 27:00.380
and I've been so busy.

27:01.070 --> 27:02.660
But you look very well.

27:03.090 --> 27:03.850
Auntie, you must be

27:03.850 --> 27:05.250
recovering well, right?

27:05.500 --> 27:06.900
If you feel unwell anywhere,

27:06.900 --> 27:07.630
just tell me.

27:07.750 --> 27:08.810
When I go back to Beijing this time,

27:08.810 --> 27:09.790
I'll go find some experts

27:09.790 --> 27:10.520
and ask them.

27:10.790 --> 27:11.900
No need.

27:12.400 --> 27:13.460
I'm fine now.

27:13.530 --> 27:14.570
It's just that Zhuang Zhuang

27:14.570 --> 27:16.110
won't let me leave the hospital.

27:16.110 --> 27:17.620
Look how bored I am.

27:18.110 --> 27:21.150
I can only knit to pass the time.

27:21.510 --> 27:23.370
This is delicate craftsmanship.

27:23.510 --> 27:25.090
And it helps you calm your mind.

27:25.090 --> 27:26.090
It's good for you.

27:29.570 --> 27:30.980
It's just that lately,

27:32.570 --> 27:34.370
it's been hard on Zhuang Zhuang.

27:35.880 --> 27:37.140
She even missed

27:37.140 --> 27:39.420
the singing competition
she was longing for

27:39.420 --> 27:41.420
to stay by my side and take care of me.

27:41.610 --> 27:42.200
Auntie,

27:42.610 --> 27:43.990
you can't say that.

27:44.380 --> 27:46.040
Zhuang Zhuang always tells me

27:46.050 --> 27:47.580
her biggest regret is

27:47.790 --> 27:49.420
not being able to be by your side.

27:49.420 --> 27:50.250
When we talked on the phone
a couple of days ago,

27:50.250 --> 27:51.250
she told me again.

27:51.400 --> 27:51.960
She said

27:52.010 --> 27:53.330
being by your side these days

27:53.330 --> 27:54.930
makes her feel very at peace.

27:55.240 --> 27:56.620
You shouldn't let
your imagination run wild.

27:56.620 --> 27:58.110
You must focus on recovering.

27:58.110 --> 27:59.070
Okay.

28:02.220 --> 28:02.820
By the way,

28:03.240 --> 28:05.480
how many days are you staying here?

28:05.980 --> 28:07.340
Zhuang Zhuang told me

28:07.690 --> 28:09.890
that you really love our southern food.

28:10.460 --> 28:12.760
The crabs are in season right now.

28:13.070 --> 28:15.110
When I am discharged in a few days,

28:16.660 --> 28:19.390
I'd like to invite you home for a meal.

28:22.000 --> 28:22.610
Auntie,

28:23.090 --> 28:24.640
there might not be a chance this time.

28:24.640 --> 28:26.370
I'm leaving in a couple of days.

28:27.660 --> 28:28.610
Next month,

28:28.960 --> 28:30.620
I'll come to see you again.

28:30.900 --> 28:32.180
You can cook yourself then

28:32.180 --> 28:33.460
and show off your skills.

28:33.460 --> 28:35.940
Zhuang Zhuang has been
tempting me for a long time, too.

28:35.940 --> 28:36.560
Okay.

28:36.640 --> 28:38.180
Since we've met,

28:38.480 --> 28:39.960
let Zhuang Zhuang take you

28:40.000 --> 28:41.930
to the old street to eat something.

28:42.010 --> 28:42.870
Zhuang Zhuang,

28:43.010 --> 28:45.500
take Shengli to eat drunken shrimp.

28:46.940 --> 28:49.130
I don't know if you'll be used to it.

28:49.180 --> 28:50.540
I'll be fine.

28:50.850 --> 28:52.010
Drunken shrimp, right?

28:52.010 --> 28:53.070
I'm very used to it.

28:54.180 --> 28:56.190
Zhuang Zhuang's always testing me,

28:56.310 --> 28:57.580
so I'm very used to it.

28:59.750 --> 29:00.310
Alright.

29:01.030 --> 29:02.050
Rest a little longer.

29:02.050 --> 29:03.240
I'll take him to eat.

29:03.660 --> 29:04.140
Okay.

29:04.200 --> 29:06.010
Then take him to the old street

29:06.110 --> 29:08.310
and have some of our local specialties.

29:08.310 --> 29:09.200
Eat more.

29:09.400 --> 29:10.350
Order a bit more.

29:10.370 --> 29:11.130
Don't worry.

29:12.900 --> 29:14.160
I'll go tell the nurse.

29:15.250 --> 29:16.140
Go ahead.

29:16.180 --> 29:17.780
Don't worry about me. Hurry.

29:32.030 --> 29:32.700
Auntie,

29:34.090 --> 29:36.330
try hard to eat and sleep well.

29:37.090 --> 29:38.950
Don't think about anything else.

29:39.810 --> 29:41.440
Zhuang Zhuang is used to carrying

29:41.440 --> 29:43.300
everything on her own shoulders.

29:43.310 --> 29:44.970
That's just her personality.

29:45.510 --> 29:46.440
But don't worry.

29:46.980 --> 29:47.850
From now on,

29:48.570 --> 29:49.900
I will carry it with her.

29:56.090 --> 29:57.050
I won't worry.

30:17.810 --> 30:19.820
I see that Auntie's mental state

30:19.920 --> 30:20.720
is quite good.

30:22.960 --> 30:24.220
The surgery went well.

30:25.030 --> 30:26.870
Now we'll see how the recovery goes.

30:26.870 --> 30:30.660
[Hotel]

30:35.750 --> 30:38.280
The old street
my mom mentioned is just ahead.

30:43.790 --> 30:44.650
Zhuang Zhuang.

30:56.070 --> 30:56.930
Zhuang Zhuang.

30:59.660 --> 31:00.300
I'm sorry.

31:03.420 --> 31:04.480
Back then,

31:04.880 --> 31:07.480
I thought you might have
run into some trouble,

31:07.920 --> 31:09.380
but I really didn't expect

31:09.440 --> 31:11.700
you'd have to face a situation like this.

31:11.830 --> 31:13.290
But thinking about it now,

31:13.750 --> 31:15.290
I even forced you to

31:15.750 --> 31:17.350
participate in the singing competition.

31:17.350 --> 31:18.800
Without realizing it,

31:18.850 --> 31:20.290
I made you more stressed.

31:22.590 --> 31:23.480
I'm sorry.

31:25.440 --> 31:26.570
It's not your fault.

31:28.240 --> 31:29.770
I didn't tell you in time.

31:39.290 --> 31:40.090
I only brought

31:40.110 --> 31:41.910
this much cash with me this time.

31:42.010 --> 31:43.720
I didn't bring my bankbook either.

31:43.720 --> 31:46.450
I'll transfer you more
when I get back to Beijing.

31:52.660 --> 31:53.590
I knew

31:54.740 --> 31:56.740
you definitely wouldn't accept it.

31:59.220 --> 32:00.870
We know each other too well.

32:05.140 --> 32:06.200
But think about it.

32:06.530 --> 32:07.250
If

32:08.790 --> 32:10.360
I were the one in trouble,

32:11.090 --> 32:12.270
would you help me?

32:17.790 --> 32:19.430
We're of the same age,

32:20.050 --> 32:21.450
and we both have parents.

32:22.000 --> 32:23.000
Don't be stubborn

32:28.000 --> 32:29.550
with me about this.

32:31.110 --> 32:32.880
Auntie's health comes first.

32:47.380 --> 32:48.050
Thank you.

32:49.050 --> 32:49.900
It's nothing.

32:56.740 --> 32:57.820
How long are you

32:57.850 --> 32:58.940
staying this time?

32:59.510 --> 33:01.770
I'm leaving the morning after tomorrow.

33:04.070 --> 33:04.950
One more thing.

33:06.240 --> 33:07.100
Zhuang Zhuang,

33:07.980 --> 33:10.240
no matter what happens to you from now on,

33:10.660 --> 33:11.810
you must tell me,

33:13.680 --> 33:14.420
okay?

33:26.660 --> 33:28.110
Let's go get something to eat.

33:28.110 --> 33:28.810
No need.

33:29.790 --> 33:30.460
It's so late.

33:30.460 --> 33:31.790
You've had a long day at the hospital.

33:31.790 --> 33:32.920
Let me walk you home.

33:35.030 --> 33:36.430
My house is right nearby.

33:39.810 --> 33:40.330
Okay.

33:41.570 --> 33:42.970
I'll be heading back now.

33:50.140 --> 33:51.600
Zhuang Zhuang, don't cry.

33:52.010 --> 33:52.970
Everything

33:53.000 --> 33:54.440
is moving in a good direction now,

33:54.440 --> 33:55.060
isn't it?

33:56.140 --> 33:58.010
Okay, then I'll be going.

34:42.360 --> 34:42.889
Xiaobao.

34:43.260 --> 34:44.010
Sis Ranran,

34:44.340 --> 34:46.540
my mother made this especially for you.

34:48.920 --> 34:50.719
Smell it. Doesn't it smell good?

34:57.510 --> 34:58.650
Sis, what's wrong?

35:00.730 --> 35:01.440
I'm fine.

35:02.000 --> 35:03.800
Please thank your mother for me.

35:04.730 --> 35:05.230
Okay.

35:05.960 --> 35:07.090
Are you really okay?

35:21.350 --> 35:22.080
There.

35:23.670 --> 35:24.830
For the growing boy.

35:25.550 --> 35:26.280
You're back.

35:27.170 --> 35:28.800
Come, eat.

35:35.010 --> 35:36.170
Did she like it?

35:38.480 --> 35:40.110
She threw up.

35:41.650 --> 35:42.180
Threw up?

35:45.790 --> 35:47.660
But this dish smells really good.

35:48.840 --> 35:49.440
Let me try.

35:59.760 --> 36:00.760
It's pretty good.

36:03.710 --> 36:05.030
She threw up?

37:01.010 --> 37:02.760
What's wrong?

37:02.820 --> 37:04.150
Are you feeling unwell?

37:05.460 --> 37:06.630
Something's with Ranran.

37:06.630 --> 37:08.320
That's not how you throw up
when you're sick.

37:08.320 --> 37:13.030
I was pregnant with Xiaobao, I know.

37:16.170 --> 37:17.340
You mean

37:18.480 --> 37:19.210
Ranran is...

37:19.340 --> 37:19.940
Pregnant?

37:24.440 --> 37:25.210
Chu Caiyuan!

37:25.230 --> 37:26.840
-Get out of the car!
-You again?

37:26.840 --> 37:27.850
Get out of the car!

37:27.920 --> 37:28.340
Are you ever going to stop?

37:28.340 --> 37:28.860
Security!

37:28.860 --> 37:29.860
Get out of the car!

37:30.480 --> 37:31.810
Won't you give it a rest?

37:31.900 --> 37:34.460
Get out, you scumbag!

37:34.760 --> 37:35.650
Don't talk nonsense.

37:35.650 --> 37:36.560
He knows

37:36.590 --> 37:37.870
what he did.

37:38.190 --> 37:40.350
You ruined a girl's life!

37:40.510 --> 37:41.550
You scumbag!

37:41.550 --> 37:42.560
Get out of the car!

37:43.320 --> 37:44.230
Get out!

37:45.210 --> 37:46.570
Get out!

38:05.480 --> 38:06.320
Mr. Guo.

38:07.650 --> 38:08.230
Mr. Guo.

38:10.800 --> 38:11.400
What's up?

38:12.070 --> 38:13.400
Northeasterner told me you got hurt.

38:13.400 --> 38:14.210
What happened?

38:14.210 --> 38:14.890
I'm fine.

38:14.920 --> 38:16.230
I was working

38:16.230 --> 38:17.570
and accidentally

38:17.900 --> 38:19.430
pulled my back.

38:21.420 --> 38:22.220
It's nothing.

38:24.360 --> 38:25.890
What happened to your face?

38:26.010 --> 38:26.610
I- I...

38:26.780 --> 38:29.130
I just took a fall.

38:36.210 --> 38:37.180
It's nothing.

38:39.030 --> 38:40.570
Did you go find Chu Caiyuan?

38:46.550 --> 38:48.260
I just couldn't stand it.

38:49.190 --> 38:52.500
How could he bully you like this?

38:55.480 --> 38:57.400
It's nothing.

38:58.050 --> 38:59.260
I'm fine.

39:06.500 --> 39:07.890
Where else are you hurt? Let me see.

39:07.890 --> 39:09.420
I'm fine. I'm really fine.

39:19.420 --> 39:20.350
I'll go find him.

39:20.710 --> 39:21.310
Ranran,

39:21.760 --> 39:22.840
don't go.

39:24.590 --> 39:25.610
If you go,

39:26.280 --> 39:28.740
I would have taken
this beating for nothing.

39:29.280 --> 39:29.960
Right?

39:30.460 --> 39:31.490
I went to see him

39:32.190 --> 39:33.930
because I didn't want

39:34.530 --> 39:36.530
him to harass you

39:36.550 --> 39:37.780
or see you again.

39:40.640 --> 39:42.100
Then I'll call the police.

39:42.880 --> 39:44.280
No, no, you can't.

39:46.190 --> 39:47.190
This matter

39:51.730 --> 39:53.660
cannot be blown out of proportion.

39:58.070 --> 40:00.860
Come, sit with me for a while.

40:14.170 --> 40:15.090
About this,

40:16.400 --> 40:19.980
don't tell your aunt.

40:21.440 --> 40:24.110
Don't mention it to Xiaobao either.

40:31.940 --> 40:32.400
Mr. Guo,

40:36.900 --> 40:37.990
I feel so wronged.

40:41.570 --> 40:43.020
It's okay, girl.

40:45.690 --> 40:50.960
Let's sit and get some air.

40:59.590 --> 41:00.650
Get some fresh air.

41:05.340 --> 41:05.840
Wang,

41:06.360 --> 41:08.670
make sure these workers
eat and drink well.

41:08.670 --> 41:09.340
Take good care of them.

41:09.340 --> 41:09.650
Okay.

41:09.650 --> 41:10.280
Go quickly.

41:10.280 --> 41:11.610
Don't worry, Director.

41:19.640 --> 41:20.510
Yang,

41:20.820 --> 41:21.480
what's wrong?

41:21.480 --> 41:22.780
We are about to return to Beijing.

41:22.780 --> 41:24.860
We need to hurry back and find workers.

41:24.860 --> 41:25.660
What workers?

41:26.070 --> 41:27.790
Aren't all the workers here?

41:28.260 --> 41:29.030
They are?

41:29.860 --> 41:31.980
Ye called me yesterday.

41:32.530 --> 41:34.820
He said it was about your business.

41:35.030 --> 41:35.960
I thought, "Wow,

41:36.070 --> 41:37.840
what a small world."

41:38.050 --> 41:39.150
Yay? What "Yay"?

41:40.190 --> 41:41.130
Not yay.

41:41.440 --> 41:42.000
Ye.

41:42.000 --> 41:43.360
Ye from Cotton Mill No. 2.

41:43.360 --> 41:43.920
He said his daughter

41:43.920 --> 41:45.380
is your friend in Beijing.

41:47.000 --> 41:48.260
Zhuang Zhuang, right?

41:48.760 --> 41:49.690
That's not Ye.

41:49.690 --> 41:51.000
That's your father-in-law.

41:51.000 --> 41:51.610
What father-in-law?

41:51.610 --> 41:52.610
Don't talk nonsense.

41:52.610 --> 41:54.070
Ye really is capable.

41:54.940 --> 41:55.590
He got all these workers

41:55.590 --> 41:56.550
back here.

41:57.070 --> 41:58.270
Now that we have them,

41:58.630 --> 42:00.610
our factory can take orders again.

42:01.070 --> 42:01.640
Yes.

42:01.780 --> 42:03.090
That's great.

42:04.070 --> 42:04.600
Shengli,

42:05.380 --> 42:06.630
about what you said last time,

42:06.630 --> 42:08.290
I thought about it carefully.

42:08.500 --> 42:09.960
Now that all the workers are here,

42:09.960 --> 42:11.220
I feel more confident.

42:11.710 --> 42:12.320
You don't need to

42:12.320 --> 42:14.120
pay the 50,000 deposit anymore.

42:14.280 --> 42:15.810
You have 30,000,

42:16.150 --> 42:17.110
and you're

42:17.130 --> 42:18.050
a Beijing man who has

42:18.050 --> 42:18.910
been to Russia.

42:18.940 --> 42:20.630
Ensure the quality of the leather for me.

42:20.630 --> 42:21.860
Once the machines are fixed,

42:21.860 --> 42:23.590
we will start full production.

42:24.480 --> 42:26.400
You still want 30,000
despite being confident?

42:26.400 --> 42:27.130
Don't worry.

42:27.190 --> 42:28.440
I will definitely
deliver the deposit and leather

42:28.440 --> 42:29.570
to you on time.

42:29.860 --> 42:30.790
B-Brother Yang.

42:31.000 --> 42:33.130
Although our order is small this time,

42:33.130 --> 42:34.730
we must ensure both quality and quantity.

42:34.730 --> 42:35.880
We are going to export them.

42:35.880 --> 42:37.610
Every product of ours represents

42:37.610 --> 42:39.050
China's international image.

42:39.050 --> 42:40.300
Oh my, those words

42:40.320 --> 42:41.380
got me all fired up.

42:41.500 --> 42:42.130
Shengli,

42:42.360 --> 42:43.610
you don't know well enough

42:43.610 --> 42:44.940
what kind of person I am.

42:45.130 --> 42:46.000
The quality of the product

42:46.000 --> 42:46.930
is our lifeline.

42:47.440 --> 42:48.530
I will definitely do a good job.

42:48.530 --> 42:49.550
You can rest assured.

42:49.550 --> 42:50.360
How about this?

42:50.360 --> 42:51.570
Let's meet the workers

42:51.570 --> 42:52.440
and encourage them.

42:52.440 --> 42:52.820
Okay?

42:52.940 --> 42:53.340
Hurry.

42:53.630 --> 42:54.230
Come here.

42:54.320 --> 42:55.110
-Well…
-Come in.

42:55.110 --> 42:56.370
-Come on.
-Now you’ve got me stumped.
